                    <li>Helps improve skin texture and reduce the appearance of hyperpigmentation.</li>
                    <li>Lightweight, non-sticky formula that absorbs quickly and layers well.</li>
                    <li>Formulated with soothing botanicals to calm and comfort the skin.</li>
                </ul>
            {{/c-suggest-card }}
            {{#> c-suggest-card
                title="Neck & Décolletage LED Device"
                image="sections/isolated/skincare-plan/images/neck-prod.webp"
                image-hover="/sections/isolated/skincare-plan/images/hov_img_4.webp"
                results="sections/isolated/skincare-plan/images/neck-result.webp"
                desc="A targeted LED light therapy device designed specifically for the delicate skin on your neck and chest."
                video="W9KXAimjHCE"
                quot-strong="I’m surprised how much younger my neck looks"
                quot-small="and my skin looks and feels more rejuvenated."
                id="suggestCardDecolletage"
            }}
