                    <li>Uses wavelengths of LED light that have been clinically proven to support skin clarity and repair.</li>
                    <li>Helps even skin tone and improve the feel of firmness.</li>
                    <li>Pairs seamlessly with Qure’s Micro-Infusion for enhanced results.</li>
                </ul>
            {{/c-suggest-card }}
